<br>
Got one group where an SK was the puller, Decent group at start, then the SK sits down after pulling some, I ask if the cleric and slower have mana. They say yes fom. I ask why he is not pulling..... He says he needs mana to pull or he will die. Ok now this is just stupid for a number of a reason but I wont go into them, So then the cleric tells me to twitch him....... Because he can not pull without mana or he will die... &quot;Oddly I can run up smack something with my scythe and pull it back to the group alive with only 2063hp.&quot;<br>
I say no insted I will pull, I pull one the SK throws a huge fit that he is the puller and I need to twitch him.... I left that group fast and soloed right bye them 3X faster then they pulled cause they had to wait for his gimp ass to get mana.<br>
<br>
1. Necromancers CAN pull and easyly split with snare + fd + force shield &quot;750 pt free rune.<br>
<br>
Now onto another thing I had happen, I got a group that wanted to hit veksar, We sat at the ent they said we have to have a slower...... I told them I could slow undead. They said necro slow is not good enough, I have a guildie bst lord comeing to slow it should work. Well needless to say the bst lord stoped slowing because mine over rids his.<br>
<br>
2. Necromancers CAN slow undead to 70% &quot;shaman slow is 75 I think, bst 50, bard 50ish give or take some I think.&quot;<br>
Necromancers can also mez undead up to level 65.<br>
<br>
Recently I got a group in BOT. They insisted we could not do names without mana regen, I told them I had mind wrack, they ignored it because they did not know what it was, After 45 mins trying to explain to them what it was we hit the named, cleric ended fight FoM<br>
<br>
3 Necromacers can GROUP lifetap and GROUP mana tap for 300 mana to each member &quot;also takes the mobs mana away so it can't cast as much.&quot;<br>
<br>
This part is just a normal problem that happens alot. I use my hp to mana conversion then I use my lifetap dot much like a shaman does cannib + torpor. The problem is my hp drops more slow, Due to this healers seem to like to waste there mana healing me to turn around and say OOM.<br>
<br>
4 Do not heal necromancers unless they are being hit, If they are being hit and the mob stops hitting them befor you heal, stop, can lifetap hp back so long as crap ain't pounding on us.<br>
<br>
Probly the biggest problem that pisses me off the most is when groups consider a wizard higher dps then a necro. A necro is ALLWAYS higher dps then a wizard over a long duration, Wizards just spike high DPS then med for a few mins, We keep dps on a target all the time, Wizards still have there place, If you need to drop a mob fast they rock but for crying out loud nukeing 1-3 times a fight is no where near the dps of me + my pet. Many many logs showing necros average 100-150 dps WITHOUT pet in groups where they are not focusing totaly on dps andcan spike over 200 DPS when nukeing + dotting, Pet does around 60-70 DPS at 65.<br>
<br>
5 Necros are effective as a dps class.<br>
<br>
God I could go on about a ton more stuff but I won't......<br>
The fact is that people really need to learn more about other classes or be open to trying them.<br>
<br>
So group a necro next time =/ Sure we can solo but some of us like to group to!!!!<br>
And remmeber groups love &lt;3 mind wrack &lt;3<br>
