Actually, a wise Shadow Knight will keep some mana in reserve just in case they need to FD a bad pull, so gonna have to shoot down that statement, and if they are main tank, its good too keep mana in reserve for Terror line, (Terror of Death, Terror of Shadows, etc)...<br>
